		(layer "F.Cu")
		(uuid "a855d1c1-169f-41ed-99a8-7aeca5626ca2")
		(at 69.65 30)
		(descr "TDK InvenSense ICM-42688-P 6-axis IMU LGA-14 package. Body 3.0x2.5x0.91 mm; 14 pads at 0.5 mm pitch. Pad geometry 0.975 x 0.25 mm per IPC-7351B Density-N for 0.5 mm pitch LGA; pad-edge gap 0.25 mm in pitch direction clears the 0.2 mm netclass clearance. Pin layout per TDK DS-000347 Figure 5. Cross-verified geometry against community footprints Gripsou/effective-coffee-spoon CC-BY-SA-4.0 and Aerokitties/Kitties-Hardware unlicensed and tetra-aero/ICM-42688-P_breakout GPL-3.0 reference only. Production evidence: ARK Electronics ARKV6X open-source FC MIT licensed at github.com/ARK-Electronics/ARKV6X_Flight_Controller uses dual ICM-42688-P in this exact LGA-14 package. Built from package mechanical dimensions in TDK DS-000347 section 11.1 public datasheet; not copied from any single-source community footprint. Recommended TDK land pattern from controlled-distribution AN-IVS-0002A-00 not directly available - see OPEN_QUESTIONS phase4a-1 - but IPC-7351B Density-N matches the LGA-14 industry-standard pattern. Datasheet URL https://invensense.tdk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/DS-000347-ICM-42688-P-v1.6.pdf")
